ihs.apcs.spacebattle.commands

Class SelfDestructCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • ihs.apcs.spacebattle.commands.ShipCommand
      • ihs.apcs.spacebattle.commands.SelfDestructCommand

  • public class SelfDestructCommand
extends ShipCommand
    A command to "self-destruct" a ship by disconnecting it from the server.

    Note: This command is not actually sent to the server. It is intercepted by the client and interpreted as a request to disconnect rather than send a new command.
